masher
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a lady-kill(er), seems to come into fashion ca1906 (cf Truth No. 41), remain for a few years, and disappear.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
